overview_description.description:
Algatechologies is a biotechnology company specialized in the commercial cultivation of microalgae. It produces and supplies AstaPure, a premium natural astaxanthin.

Algatechologies was founded in 1998 and is headquartered in Eilot, HaDarom, Israel.
